RSMVC (beta)

Setup:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
 ~ Make /system/tmp/ and any subfolders writable (chmod 777)
 ~ Edit the config: /config/config.php


Code/file conventions:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
Models
 ~ /application/models/ExampleNameModel.php
 ~ class ExampleNameModel extends Model
 ~ To create a database instance: Database::getInstance()

Controllers
 ~ /application/controllers/ExampleNameController.php
 ~ class ExampleNameController extends Controller

Views
 ~ /application/views/example_name.php

URLs
 ~ URL's may only contain lowercase alphanumeric characters, - and /